Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,NEON GENESIS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Like a cruel angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...young boy, become a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Even though the blue wind knocked at the door of your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...you kept looking and smiling only at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lost while searching for something soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...your honest eyes show that you haven't realized your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But someday, you'll recognize that on your back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...you have the wings to fly to the distant future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A cruel revelation from the angels will fly out from a window soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,When you deny your memory with your spurting and burning pathos...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shine and hold up the sky.  Young boy, become a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Second and third Ashino Lakes...\NI hope there's no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Chairman Keel complained to me directly about the delay of the project yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He was very frustrated.\NHe even mentioned dismissing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Adam's progressing smoothly. The Eva project has progressed to the dummy plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why are those old\Nmen of Seele so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And more importantly, the Human Complement Project's behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All projects are mutually linked.\NIt'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,About Rei, also?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,By the way, what're you\Ngoing to do with "him?''
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll leave him alone\Njust like Marduk Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's still useful for\Na while longer, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kyoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What was begun here\Nsixteen years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Episode 15
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A Lie and Silence\N"uso to chinmoku''
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:03:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shanon Bio...\Nit's a foreign chemical company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It was established here 9 years ago,\Nand it hasn't changed in 9 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,106 out of 108 companies connected to the Marduk Agency are dummies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And that's the 107th,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is the registration\Nof the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're gonna say, "Look at the names of the executive officers,'' right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I already know\Nthose names.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The Marduk Agency, which was established to choose the pilots for Evangelion...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...is an advisory organization under the Human Complement Committee's direct control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Details of the organization\Nare still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your duty is to investigate NERV. It's not advisable to meddle with the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, I won't be satisfied unless\NI confirm everything myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hello, this is Kaji. I'm out now.\NPlease leave a message if you need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Help me, Kaji!\NWhat're you doing, you pervert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Tomorrow's Sunday, and I wanted Kaji to take me somewhere, so I called him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...but he's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's been out every time\NI've called him these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That means you're\Nfree tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Unfortunately, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want to ask\Nyou a little favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Date...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's my sister Kodama's friend.\NI was asked to introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do it seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Cleaning is what you\Nshould do seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Necrosis procedure is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The reversible graph,\Nmeasuring complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What are you going\Nto wear tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,For the wedding reception...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I wore a pink suit\Nat Kiyomi's reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I just wore the deep\Nblue dress at Kotoko's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What about the orange one?\NYou haven't worn it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, that one...? \NI can't wear it for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Too tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Damn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'd better\Nbuy a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've had to\Nspend a lot recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lately, it's been happening one after another. The cost of gifts isn't going down either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They must've rushed it\Nsince they're almost thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Neither you nor I want to be the last ones, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All three of you\Ncan come back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm tired of tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come to think of it, Shinji looked depressed more than usual today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because "it'' is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's right,\N"it'' is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have to see\Nmy father tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you think\NI should talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because I've seen you\N talking cheerfully to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Can you tell me...what kind\Nof person is my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is that why you've been\Nstaring at me, to ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,At cleaning time you were wringing the dust cloth, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You looked motherly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It looked like it was a\Nmother's way of wringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Actually, you may be suited\Nto being a housewife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Get to bed. You have a date tomorrow, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, with a\N"handsome'' guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, that's right.\NCan I use your lavender perfume?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's not for children.\NIs Shinji in his room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He hasn't come out at all. He doesn't seem to want to see his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If he doesn't want to, why doesn't he say so? Japanese are always...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It doesn't mean that he doesn't want to. And that's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good job, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shinji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you afraid of\Nseeing your father alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You shouldn't\Nkeep running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...but you have to step forward\Nor nothing'll change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You'll discover the importance of going forward once you've taken the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Anyway, be confident tomorrow.\NYou're going to see your mother as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You bought a dress for tomorrow, right?\NLet me see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You wanna see it?\NIt was expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your sense is more\Nimportant than the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you pick one\Nthat Kaji would like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, I don't now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Three bags in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Red, blue and yellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well then, please take\Nsome time to talk freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ryo-chan hasn't showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That idiot never\Nshows up on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,For dating, right?\NHe does when he's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, you two are as\Nbeautiful as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I couldn't finish\Nmy job in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Despite that, you're\Nalways killing time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Besides, why're\Nyou always unshaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, your tie's loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You guys look like\Na married couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm pleased to\Nhear that, Rit-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why would we be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's been three years\Nsince we visited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I ran away back then,\Nand I haven't come back until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't feel like\Nmy mother's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't remember\Nher face either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,People live by\Nforgetting the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But there are things\Nyou shouldn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yui taught me\Nthat important fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I come here\Nto reaffirm that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't you have any photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No. This tombstone's ornamental.\NThere was no body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You threw everything away, just like my teacher said, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Everything's inside my heart.\NThat's enough for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's time.\NI'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...well, I'm glad that\NI could talk to you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,NEON GENESIS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Not bad at all. I didn't know you could do stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I can only play this well because I started when I was five...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...I don't have\Nmuch talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't they say, "persistence is a virtue?''\NI have a better impression of you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I started playing because\Nmy teacher suggested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I could have\Ngiven it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Then, why'd you\Nkeep playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because no one\Ntold me to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're home early. I thought\Nyou were going to eat supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He was boring, so I left him while we were waiting for the roller coaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's pretty rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kaji's the only nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What're you talking about?\NI'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,High-heels...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,When was the last\Ntime we drank together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Misato's been drinking too much.\NShe seems happy for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Drink to hide your cheerful self...\NToday, I might be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The person who lived with her\Nsays something convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We lived together, but that's before she put on high-heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We couldn't imagine that\Nwhen we were in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:13:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I was young, and we were simply staying in the same place. It was like playing house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The reality isn't so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, this is\Nfor your cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thanks.\NYou're so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Only to women.\NMy work's sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I wonder.\NTo Misato, also?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I bought a farm once. I won't join a losing war. That's my policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I think you have\Na winning strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What about you, Rit-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have a policy not to talk about myself,\Nbecause it's not very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She's late. I wonder if\Nshe's touching up her makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why did you\Ngo to Kyoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, that's\Nfrom Matsushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't play innocent. If you go too far, your fingers will get burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm giving you a warning,\Nas a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll listen. It's okay if I get burned while I'm playing with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Should I buy you\Nsome fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your fickle personality\Nhasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes, it has.\NTo live is to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's homeostasis\Nand transistasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The forces to maintain or\Nchange the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We have both of those conflicting characteristics at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Like a man and woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'd better go home.\NI still have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Really?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shin-chan...?\NIt's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm drinking with Kaji.\NYes, we're holding a third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay...okay...bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah. She said she'll be late\Nand to go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She's not coming home\Ntomorrow morning, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She can't be because\NKaji's with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you stupid?!\NThat's why I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Grownups usually don't puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sorry about being\Nold already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're the same age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're wearing high-heels.\NI really feel like time has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why don't you shave?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll walk.  Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kaji, have I changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You've become more beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm sorry that I said\Ngoodbye back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I told you I fell in love with another guy, but it was a lie. Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I noticed that\Nyou were like my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I was longing for\Nmy father in men.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,When I noticed that,\NI was scared, so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:16:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Staying with you, being a woman.\NEverything was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hated my father, but I fell in love with a man like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I joined NERV\Nto forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But it's the organization my father once belonged to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I was deceiving myself by\Ntaking revenge against Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You've chosen to do that.\NYou don't have to apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, I didn't choose!\NI was simply running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I ran away from the\Nchains called "father.''
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's just like Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm really sorry to say such things,\Nthough it's because I'm drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm so childish. I have no\Nright to preach to Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm hypocritical because I rely on a man at my convenience, just like now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I might have used you back then!\NI hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's enough. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm so disappointed\Nin myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey Shinji,\Ndo you want to kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kiss, you know, a kiss.\NYou haven't kissed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Then, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because it's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"Boring,'' you said...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You don't want to kiss on the anniversary of your mom's death, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you think she might\Nbe watching us from Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, I'm not\Nscared of kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You brushed your teeth,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Then, here I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't breathe through\Nyour nose, it tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:19:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yuck! I shouldn't have done it\Nto kill time after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, we're home.\NHang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why don't you stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They'll laugh at me if\NI go to work looking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right, Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The smell of lavender...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You two, take care\Nof Katsuragi, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good night.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What's wrong?\NYou look disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's because I kissed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, girls are next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ayanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is Ayanami absent today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,NERV Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The center of the deep\Nunderground facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Central Dogma
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Same location.\N2008 meters under ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Terminal Dogma
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How's your hangover?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's gone, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is this your true job?\NOr just part time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kaji Ryouji belongs to the Special Inspection Division of the Special Institute, NERV...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:21:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...but you also belong to Japan's Ministry of the Interior, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You knew, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't underestimate NERV.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Did Commander Ikari order you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, this's my own act.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If you continue your part time job any further, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Commander Ikari's making use of me.\NI'll continue for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But I apologize to you\Nfor keeping this a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll cancel this to show\Nmy thanks for last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thanks. But the Commander, and even Rit-chan, kept this a secret from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No...it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes, it's the key to\Neverything since the Second Impact...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...and it was the\Nbeginning as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Adam...?\NThe First Angel is here...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Surely, NERV can't\Nbe taken lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,TO BE CONTINUED
