Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shinji: Megumi Ogata~~~\N\N~Misato: Kotono Mitsuishi\N\NRitsuko: Yuriko Yamaguchi\N\N~~~~~~Rei: Megumi Hayashibara\N\NAsuka: Yuko Miyamura~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,~~Gendou: Fumihiko Tachiki\N\NFuyutsuki: Genmu Kiyokawa~~~\N\N~~Ryouji: Kouichi Yamadera\N\NTouji: Tomokazu Seki\N\NHikari: Junko Iwao~~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Woman: Miki Nagasawa\N\N~~Host: Kouichi Nagano
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ikari Shinji finally surpasses Asuka, and scores the highest in the synchro test.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,However, his overconfidence\Ndraws him into Dirac's Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The limited time of survival\Nwill teach him despair.
